value.name: Magia Record: Puella Magi Madoka Magica Side Story
value.original_name: マギアレコード 魔法少女まどか☆マギカ外伝
value.overview: Few people know the truth: the world is safe thanks to the Magical Girls who are forced to slay Witches. Even though these girls are putting their lives on the line for a wish, rumors say they can be saved in Kamihama City. That’s where Iroha Tamaki is headed in search of answers; she can’t remember the wish she made to Kyubey.
